00:00:25.810 --> 00:00:30.609
of the time it's oil leaking, and then
getting on the exhaust, and then make it

00:00:30.609 --> 00:00:35.470
a little burning smell, now in this case
we'll take off the stupid beauty cover, and

00:00:35.470 --> 00:00:38.949
