we'll see there's oil leaking all the

00:00:38.949 --> 00:00:46.210
way under it, and when we go under the
car, we can see oils dripped the whole way

00:00:46.210 --> 00:00:50.320
down, starting at the top dripped all the
way down, so it's time for new valve

00:00:50.320 --> 00:00:54.670
cover gaskets, and as you can see here,
the oils got on the exhaust pipe and

00:00:54.670 --> 00:00:57.370
of course this gets really hot when the
cars run, and then that's where most of

00:00:57.370 --> 00:01:02.500
the smell will be coming from, now in the
case of this v6 Lexus the front valve

00:01:02.500 --> 00:01:08.200
cover is pretty easy to get to, but,
behind the front cover gasket is the

00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:12.369
back cover gasket, inside here we got to
